@page "/components/data-table"

<PageTitle>Data Table</PageTitle>

<RzQuickReferenceContainer>
    <RzArticle ProseWidth="ProseWidth.UltraWide">
        <SideContent>
            <RzQuickReference />
        </SideContent>
        <MainContent>
            <RzBreadcrumb class="mb-4 not-prose">
                <BreadcrumbList>
                    <BreadcrumbItem><BreadcrumbLink Href="/">Docs</BreadcrumbLink></BreadcrumbItem>
                    <BreadcrumbSeparator />
                    <BreadcrumbItem><BreadcrumbLink Href="/components">Components</BreadcrumbLink></BreadcrumbItem>
                    <BreadcrumbSeparator />
                    <BreadcrumbItem><BreadcrumbPage>Data Table</BreadcrumbPage></BreadcrumbItem>
                </BreadcrumbList>
            </RzBreadcrumb>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H1" QuickReferenceTitle="Data Table" class="scroll-mt-20">Data Table</RzHeading>
            <RzParagraph>
                <code>RzDataTable&lt;TItem&gt;</code> is an SSR-first table component that progressively enhances into TanStack-driven client state for sorting, searching, pagination, selection, and column visibility.
            </RzParagraph>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="SSR-first model" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-8">SSR-first model</RzHeading>
            <RzParagraph>
                Razor renders a meaningful fallback table for first paint and no-JS resilience. Alpine then reads inert JSON config and hands table state to TanStack Table.
            </RzParagraph>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Stable row key" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-8">Stable row key</RzHeading>
            <RzParagraph>
                You must provide <code>RowKey</code>. It is projected to <code>__key</code> and wired to TanStack <code>getRowId</code>.
            </RzParagraph>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Basic usage" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-8">Basic usage</RzHeading>
            <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor">
&lt;RzDataTable TItem="UserDto"
             Items="@@Users"
             RowKey="u =&gt; u.Id"
             Search="true"
             SelectionMode="DataTableSelectionMode.Multiple"&gt;
    &lt;DataTableColumn TItem="UserDto" Id="name" HeaderText="Name" Field="u =&gt; u.Name" Sortable="true" Searchable="true" /&gt;
    &lt;DataTableColumn TItem="UserDto" Id="email" HeaderText="Email" Field="u =&gt; u.Email" Searchable="true" /&gt;
    &lt;DataTableColumn TItem="UserDto" Id="status" HeaderText="Status" Field="u =&gt; u.Status" Sortable="true" /&gt;
&lt;/RzDataTable&gt;
            </RzCodeViewer>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Client template" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-8">Client template</RzHeading>
            <RzParagraph>
                <code>ClientTemplate</code> emits an inert HTML template once per column and is cloned client-side with <code>row</code>, <code>column</code>, and <code>cell</code> scope values.
            </RzParagraph>
            <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.Razor">
&lt;DataTableColumn TItem="UserDto" Id="status" HeaderText="Status" Field="u =&gt; u.Status" Sortable="true"&gt;
    &lt;ClientTemplate&gt;
        &lt;span class="inline-flex rounded-md px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium"
              :class="row.statusClass"
              x-text="row.statusLabel"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;/ClientTemplate&gt;
&lt;/DataTableColumn&gt;
            </RzCodeViewer>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Behavior" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-8">Behavior</RzHeading>
            <ul>
                <li>Global search is case-insensitive and only checks columns marked <code>Searchable</code>.</li>
                <li>Column visibility precedence: <code>InitialColumnVisibility</code> first, then <code>DataTableColumn.Visible</code>.</li>
                <li>Single selection uses row click; multiple selection adds header/row checkboxes.</li>
                <li>All client state is in-memory in v1 (no server mode or virtualization).</li>
            </ul>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="Events" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-8">Events</RzHeading>
            <RzCodeViewer Language="@CodeLanguage.JavaScript">
rz:datatable:ready
rz:datatable:sort-change
rz:datatable:page-change
rz:datatable:search-change
rz:datatable:column-visibility-change
rz:datatable:selection-change
rz:datatable:row-click
rz:datatable:state-change
            </RzCodeViewer>

            <RzHeading Level="HeadingLevel.H2" QuickReferenceTitle="When not to use" class="scroll-mt-20 mt-8">When not to use</RzHeading>
            <ul>
                <li>Large virtualized datasets (not in v1).</li>
                <li>Server-driven paging/sorting/filtering workflows.</li>
                <li>Complex grouping, expansion, or tree-grid interactions.</li>
            </ul>
        </MainContent>
    </RzArticle>
</RzQuickReferenceContainer>
